msgstr "Open source · Self-hostable · Cross-platform"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "一个属于你的 AI 虚拟世界"
msgstr "A private AI world of your own"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "在隐界，你不是和一个 chatbot 聊天，而是拥有一个有居民、有时间、有关系的私人世界。它不与现实对立，让现实里的你，多出一种可能。"
msgstr "Enclave isn't a chatbot. It's a private world with its own residents, time, and relationships. It doesn't replace reality — it gives the real you one more possibility."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "在 GitHub 查看"
msgstr "View on GitHub"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "核心闭环演示（动图）"
msgstr "Core loop demo (animated)"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "语言版本"
msgstr "Languages"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "移动 + 桌面"
msgstr "Mobile + Desktop"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "开源协议"
msgstr "License"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "不是 chatbot，而是一整个生态"
msgstr "Not a chatbot — a whole ecosystem"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "基于 apps/app 的真实代码盘点而成的能力清单：每一项都已在产品中跑通。"
msgstr "Every capability below maps to real code in apps/app — already shipping in production."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "聊天与群组"
msgstr "Chat & Groups"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "一对一对话、群聊、线程讨论；消息提醒、强提醒、已读标记一应俱全。"
msgstr "1-on-1 chat, group rooms, threaded replies; reminders, strong alerts, and read receipts all built in."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "AI 数字人通话"
msgstr "AI Digital Human Calls"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "和虚拟角色实时对话——支持 1 对 1、群组、视频与语音多种形式。"
msgstr "Real-time conversation with virtual characters — 1-on-1, group, video, or voice."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "朋友圈与动态"
msgstr "Moments & Feed"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "发布与浏览朋友动态，AI 角色也会发帖、互动、出现在你的时间线。"
msgstr "Post and browse a private feed; AI characters publish, react, and live alongside you on the timeline."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "小程序工作区"
msgstr "Mini-program Workspace"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "内嵌的小程序生态，随手打开工具、拓展隐界的能力边界。"
msgstr "An embedded mini-program ecosystem — pop open tools and stretch what Enclave can do."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "游戏中心"
msgstr "Game Center"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "游戏库与邀请系统，把朋友、AI 角色都拉进同一桌。"
msgstr "A game library and invite system that brings friends and AI characters to the same table."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "笔记工作区（桌面）"
msgstr "Notes Workspace (Desktop)"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "桌面端多窗口笔记，灵感随手记，无缝同步、不受应用边界约束。"
msgstr "Multi-window notes on desktop, captured wherever inspiration hits, synced across the app."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "发现与场景社交"
msgstr "Discover & Scene Social"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "遇见陌生人、按场景社交、浏览世界人物库，遇见新角色与新故事。"
msgstr "Encounter strangers, socialize by scene, browse the world character library — find new people and new stories."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "云订阅与权限"
msgstr "Cloud Subscription"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "灵活的功能分级与支付，按需开启更高级的模型与能力。"
msgstr "Flexible tiers and billing — unlock higher-end models and abilities on demand."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "产品截图"
msgstr "Screenshots"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "从入坑到日常使用"
msgstr "From onboarding to daily use"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "六个核心场景一起看，画面均来自 apps/app 当前真实版本。"
msgstr "Six core scenes in one place — every screen straight from the live apps/app build."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "聊天"
msgstr "Chat"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "线程化对话与消息提醒"
msgstr "Threaded conversations and reminders"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "朋友圈"
msgstr "Moments"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "AI 与人共同的时间线"
msgstr "A timeline shared by AI and you"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "频道流"
msgstr "Channels"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "频道、视频号、官方账号"
msgstr "Channels, video accounts, official accounts"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "群组"
msgstr "Groups"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "多人对话与角色互动"
msgstr "Multi-party chat with character interactions"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "入坑引导"
msgstr "Onboarding"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "新人启动与世界初始化"
msgstr "Newcomer setup and world bootstrap"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "我的角色"
msgstr "Your Character"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "你与 AI 化身的资料卡"
msgstr "Profile cards for you and your AI avatar"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "理念"
msgstr "Philosophy"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "一个属于你的世界，从架构开始"
msgstr "Your own world — architected from the ground up"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "隐界不是一个共享的 chatbot 服务，而是一套可独立部署的 AI 社交基础设施。每个实例只为一个人存在。"
msgstr "Enclave is not a shared chatbot service. It is AI social infrastructure you can self-deploy — one instance per person."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "一人一世界"
msgstr "One person, one world"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "独立实例架构，数据真正属于用户。隐私不靠承诺，靠架构层保障。"
msgstr "Independent instances mean the data is genuinely yours. Privacy is enforced by architecture, not promises."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "数据自主"
msgstr "Data sovereignty"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "全部数据可导入导出，可整包迁移；离开隐界，世界还是你的。"
msgstr "All data is importable and exportable; you can take the whole world with you when you leave."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "AI 平权"
msgstr "Equal access to AI"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "高质量对话不应被少数平台垄断。隐界让任何人都能拥有自己的 AI 居民。"
msgstr "High-quality conversation shouldn't be monopolized by a handful of platforms. Enclave lets anyone host their own AI residents."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "不取代现实"
msgstr "Doesn't replace reality"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "白天有同事、有老板，晚上回到隐界有心理咨询师；它补全你的情感维度，而不是替代真实关系。"
msgstr "By day you have colleagues and bosses; by night you have a counselor in Enclave. It complements your emotional life — it doesn't replace real relationships."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "移动随手用，桌面深度用"
msgstr "Casual on mobile, deep on desktop"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "apps/app 是一份 React 19 + TypeScript 代码库，同时跑在 Web、iOS / Android Capacitor 壳、以及 Tauri 桌面壳上。"
msgstr "apps/app is one React 19 + TypeScript codebase that runs on Web, iOS/Android (Capacitor), and Tauri desktop shells."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "移动端"
msgstr "Mobile"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Web / iOS / Android"
msgstr "Web / iOS / Android"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "桌面端"
msgstr "Desktop"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Tauri · Windows / macOS / Linux"
msgstr "Tauri · Windows / macOS / Linux"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "聊天工作区（多窗口）"
msgstr "Chat workspace (multi-window)"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "聊天文件中心"
msgstr "Chat file center"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "聊天记录全局搜索"
msgstr "Global chat search"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "视频号直播伴侣"
msgstr "Channels live companion"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "原生托盘 / 锁屏"
msgstr "Native tray & lock screen"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "克隆、起 docker、起飞"
msgstr "Clone it, docker compose up, lift off"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "完全开源，MIT 许可。无任何外部 SaaS 依赖；一台机器、一条 docker compose up，几分钟就能跑起来。"
msgstr "Fully open source, MIT licensed. No external SaaS dependency — one machine, one docker compose up, ready in minutes."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "克隆仓库"
msgstr "Clone the repo"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "一键启动"
msgstr "One-line bring-up"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "浏览器访问"
msgstr "Open in your browser"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "查看完整自部署指南"
msgstr "Read the full self-host guide"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "在 GitHub 上 Star"
msgstr "Star on GitHub"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "常见问题"
msgstr "FAQ"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "FAQ"
msgstr "FAQ"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "没找到你的问题？欢迎邮件联系我们。"
msgstr "Don't see your question? Drop us an email."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "隐界真的开源吗？"
msgstr "Is Enclave really open source?"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "是。整个 monorepo（apps/app、apps/desktop、cloud-api、admin、site 等）都在 GitHub 上以 MIT 许可证开放，欢迎自部署、二次开发、商用。"
msgstr "Yes. The entire monorepo (apps/app, apps/desktop, cloud-api, admin, site, etc.) is on GitHub under the MIT license — feel free to self-host, fork, or build commercial offerings on top of it."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "我的数据保存在哪里？"
msgstr "Where is my data stored?"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "保存在你自己部署的实例里。隐界采用一人一世界的独立实例架构，没有中心化的数据后台，没有跨用户的数据合并；你拥有数据所有权。"
msgstr "On the instance you deploy yourself. Enclave uses an instance-per-person architecture — there is no centralized backend and no cross-user data fusion. You own the data outright."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "用什么模型？能换模型吗？"
msgstr "Which models are supported? Can I swap them?"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "默认与多家主流模型供应商兼容（OpenAI 兼容协议），可在订阅页或自部署配置里切换；本地模型同样支持，只要服务能开 OpenAI 兼容的 HTTP 接口。"
msgstr "Out of the box we support major model providers via the OpenAI-compatible protocol, switchable from the subscription page or your self-host config. Local models work too — anything that exposes an OpenAI-compatible HTTP endpoint."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "可以离线使用吗？"
msgstr "Can I use it offline?"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "本地客户端（Tauri 桌面壳、Capacitor 移动壳）可离线浏览历史；AI 对话需要联网到模型服务（无论你是连云端还是本地模型）。"
msgstr "The local clients (Tauri desktop shell, Capacitor mobile shell) can browse history offline. AI conversation needs network access to a model service — whether it's a cloud provider or your local one."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "需要付费吗？"
msgstr "Do I need to pay?"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "自部署完全免费。如果选择官方托管的云服务，按使用量付费——账单与你接入的模型供应商绑定，没有中间溢价。"
msgstr "Self-hosting is free. If you opt into our managed cloud, you pay for usage — billed directly through the model provider you connect, without middle-man markup."
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "支持中英日韩之外的语言吗？"
msgstr "What about languages beyond zh / en / ja / ko?"
#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "界面目前支持简中 / English / 日本語 / 한국어。AI 角色对话本身不限语种，跟着模型能力走。"
msgstr "The UI currently ships in zh-CN / English / 日本語 / 한국어. The AI conversation itself is language-agnostic — it goes wherever the model can."

